title: 2 Bedroom, 1 Office Room & 1 Bathroom Flat for Rent
posting_body: ['This flat is located on 48th Avenue at Judah Street, near Ocean Beach.', 'It is conveniently located right next to the N Judah Muni line.', 'Available now for rent.', '-Newly remodeled', '-2 bedroom plus 1 office room', '-No pets', '-No smoking', '-Laundromat located next door', '-Close to public transportation: N Judah and 18 Muni lines', '-Monthly rent is $2,700', '-Security deposit is $2,700', '-One year lease required', 'To be considered, you will need the following items:', '1) Updated full credit report', '2) Current monthly pay stubs', '3) Tax return if self-employed', "4) Copy of driver's license or passport", '5) Completed and signed rental application', 'Please call Gene', 'show contact info', 'for further questions and viewing appointments, and leave a voicemail if no one answers your call.', 'No e-mail or text messages.']
